{"error":"ElevenLabs Music failed [429]: {\"detail\":{\"type\":\"rate_limit_error\",\"code\":\"concurrent_limit_exceeded\",\"message\":\"Too many concurrent requests. Your current subscription is associated with a maximum of 2 concurrent requests (running in parallel). This is done such that a single user does not overwhelm our systems and affect other users negatively. Please upgrade your subscription or contact sales if you want to increase this limit.\",\"status\":\"too_many_concurrent_requests\",\"request_id\":\"7486f1e0cc252ef43141945880589217\",\"docs_url\":\"https://elevenlabs.io/docs/eleven-api/resources/errors#rate-limiting-and-concurrency\"}}"}